org.eclipse.dataset

Class DataEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.EventObject
      • org.eclipse.dataset.DataEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class DataEvent
extends java.util.EventObject
    Event fired to diseminate information about a dataset changing. For instance if an image represents a live stream. This event is passed over web-sockets. To keep dependencies to a minimum and since it is really simple, we have added an encode and decode to JSON without the need for an API like jackson.
